President Donald J. Trump issued a Presidential Memorandum on July 22, 2019, regarding the national security and defense implications of the domestic production capability for Rare Earth Metals and Alloys. The memorandum states that the President has determined that this production capability is essential to national defense. Without Presidential action, the United States industry is unable to adequately and timely provide this production capability. The memorandum authorizes and directs the Secretary of Defense to publish this determination in the Federal Register.